                  <h2 style="color: white;">
                    Matheus De Oliveira Boscariol - Game & Full Stack Developer
                  </h2>
                  <blockquote>
                    “I build games and tools that merge creativity with
                    technology. I also experiment with cloud systems and
                    personal projects to sharpen my skills.”
                  </blockquote>
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <h3>Who Am I</h3>
                  <p>
                    I am Matheus, a hard working high school student. I also
                    make games and other software in my free time for fun and to
                    build up my portfolio. I usually focus on game development
                    but every once in a while I make other kinds of software. I
                    also love messing with cloud and servers. I also host a <a
                      href="/projects/homelab">homelab</a
                    > in my free time that is not only for fun but also serves as
                    a testing sandbox for my own creations.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    I also have my own <a
                      href="https://youtube.com/@matheusbosc">youtube channel</a
                    > where I post video devlogs, and complete programming challenges.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Some of my other hobbies include volleyball and rowing (I am
                    on my schools volleyball & rowing teams), I play the tenor
                    saxophone and a bit of piano, and I also like 3d printing.
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <h3>What I Do / Skills</h3>
                  <ul role="list">
                    <li>Game Development with Unity & C#.</li>
                    <li>Software development with python.</li>
                    <li>
                      Cloud & DevOps with Docker, Cloudflare, Github Actions,
                      Jenkins.
                    </li>
                    <li>Video Making & Editing.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="single-item">
                  <h3>Why I Do It</h3>
                  <!-- TODO: Finish This -->
