                    <li>
                      <strong>Why I make games & software:</strong> I love creating,
                      and why not combine that creating with another passion of mine,
                      computers! I also love the challenge and problem solving involved
                      in software development.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <strong>Why do I explore cloud and DevOps:</strong> I explore
                      these 2 because it allows me to, when not already available
                      to me, host and use my services where privacy, price, and availability
                      isnt an issue.
                    </li>
                    <li>
