                        >How do I approach learning & problem solving:</strong
                      > When approaching a problem to solve or something to learn,
                      I tend to look at the finished result, or imagine what it would
                      be like, and work backwards from there, reconstructing every
                      little part of my expected end goal.
                    </li>
                  </ul>
